  * New MultiCommitter class allowing the use multiple committers for the same
    crawler.
  * New configuration options for AbstractBatchCommitter and subclasses:
    * Max number of retries between commit failures
    * How long to wait between two attempts.
  * Empty folders are prediodically deleted, improving directory scanning
    and performance. 
